high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, turn tight at the door and go to the left end of the table, between the garbage bag on the floor and the end of the table.
Pick up the brown cup with a spoon in it, to the left of the white coffee mug, on the table.
Turn to your right and go to the sink, to the left of the refrigerator.
Place the cup with the spoon, in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup containing a spoon in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and turn right. Face the table on the right side.
Pick up the cup with a spoon in it, from the left side of the table.
Carry the cup and turn to the right, then the left and find the sink on the right.
Place the cup inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup from a table to a sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk all the way right to the corner of the room with the trash bag in it.
Pick up the bronze cup on the table, the one closest to the back edge.
Turn right and walk ahead and right to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink to the left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup in the sink.
